Property.name: AttachmentType
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the type of attachment, including whether it is the organisational logo or an additional attached image or document. </summary>

Property.name: Caption
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the caption that will appear on the link to this file within the CDA document. </summary>

Property.name: Content
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the binary content of the attachment. </summary>

Property.name: FileName
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the file name of the attachment. </summary>
